=== EVENT_QUANTUM_LABORATORY ===
# id: 49
# title: Quantum Laboratory
# chinese_title: 量子实验室
# category: Discovery
# mode: starmap

A floating research lab materializes from a quantum fold. Instruments hum with barely contained energy. The lead scientist offers to share their findings — for a price.

* [[Gain radical 气] Study the energy patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("气")
  气 (qì) — air, energy
* [[-30 credits, +20 hull] Purchase shield harmonics data] {requires: credits >= 30}
  ~ hull_and_fuel(20, 0)
  买 (mǎi) — buy
* [[+25 credits] Sell your star charts to them]
  ~ gain_credits(25)
  卖 (mài) — sell
* [[Risk: -10 hull or +40 credits] Tamper with the containment field]
  ~ fuel_and_credits(0, 30)
  危险 (wēixiǎn) — danger
* [[Nothing] Observe and leave quietly]
  ~ nothing
  安静 (ānjìng) — quiet
